@[simp]
theorem mem_attach_fin {n : ℕ} {s : Finset ℕ} (h : ∀ m ∈ s, m < n) {a : Fin n} : a ∈ s.attach_fin h ↔ (a : ℕ) ∈ s :=
  ⟨fun h =>
    let ⟨b, hb₁, hb₂⟩ := Multiset.mem_pmap.1 h
    hb₂ ▸ hb₁,
    fun h => Multiset.mem_pmap.2 ⟨a, h, Fin.eta _ _⟩⟩
#align mem_attach_fin mem_attach_fin
card_attach_fin:
@[simp]
theorem card_attach_fin {n : ℕ} (s : Finset ℕ) (h : ∀ m ∈ s, m < n) : (s.attach_fin h).card = s.card :=
  Multiset.card_pmap _ _ _
#align card_attach_fin card_attach_fin
